README:

+-------------------------------------------------------+
| chatgpt_cli - OpenAI-powered command-line interface   |
| for chatbot conversations.                            |
+-------------------------------------------------------+

This software uses OpenAI to generate chatbot conversations. To use this software,
you will need to sign up for an API key from OpenAI. Please visit the OpenAI website
to acquire an API key.

By using this software, you agree to the terms set forth in the LICENSE and
LEGAL.txt documents. Please read these documents carefully before using the
software.

